children.content:
1 -No access for the Business Actor of organisation B to the modeling server
2 - The organisation B don't have EA or they have another solution for which Models and Diagrams interchanged is not working quite well when based on XMI or DI
3- We want the Business Actor of organisation B contributing to producing ArchiMate model, but there is some reluctance using Modeling Plaforms which are considered as too complex (reason why acquisition of information is often made by mean of Excel)
